00:11:03,613 --> 00:11:04,746
Leonard?

237
00:11:04,747 --> 00:11:06,248
Quoi ?!

238
00:11:06,249 --> 00:11:08,984
Je pense que j'ai trouvé
le truc de Wolowitz,

239
00:11:08,985 --> 00:11:12,154
