00:15:13,045 --> 00:15:14,946
Oh, c'est fort, fort, fort, fort !

318
00:15:17,316 --> 00:15:20,051
Whoo! on le sent
vraiment passer, hein ?

319
00:15:20,052 --> 00:15:21,453
Bon, je vais y aller.

320
00:15:25,858 --> 00:15:28,894
